OL,3,CSeaside souvenir shop shuts its doors
OL,4,Cafter 181 years in same family
OL,6,FA seaside souvenir shop which pre-
OL,7,Fdates the invention of the telephone
OL,8,Fis to shut its doors after nearly two
OL,9,Fcenturies of trade.
OL,11,FMany of Scarborough's 3.9 million
OL,12,Fyearly visitors will be familiar with
OL,13,FJohn Wherritt, which was built before
OL,14,Fthe resort's iconic Grand Hotel and
OL,15,Fhas outlasted seven monarchs and 38
OL,16,Fprime ministers.
OL,18,FBut this month the "Aladdin's Cave" of
OL,19,Fknick-knacks will close for the final
OL,20,Ftime.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
