OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783788475
OL,3,CSeaside souvenir shop shuts its doors
OL,4,Cafter 181 years in same family
OL,6,FThe shop has been run by the same
OL,7,Ffamily for 181 years, opening just six
OL,8,Fyears into Queen Victoria's reign in
OL,9,F1845.
OL,11,FCurrent owners, sisters Celia Wilson
OL,12,Fand Sharon Jackson, are now retiring
OL,13,Fand putting the business up for sale -
OL,14,Falthough there are no plans to sell as
OL,15,Fa going concern.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar, Sharon said:
OL,18,F"There's a huge outpouring of love at
OL,19,Fthe moment, and there aren't many
OL,20,Fshops like ours.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783788475
OL,3,CSeaside souvenir shop shuts its doors
OL,4,Cafter 181 years in same family
OL,6,F"Where do you go where you can buy a
OL,7,Fpair of binoculars, and you can buy a
OL,8,Fsnappy gun that gives you a shock on
OL,9,Fyour finger?
OL,11,F"There's just not many places like us
OL,12,Fanymore."
OL,14,FWherritt's was originally opened as a
OL,15,Ftobacconist by the sisters' great
OL,16,Funcle, George, back in the 1840s.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
