CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783788475
OL,3,CSeaside souvenir shop shuts its doors
OL,4,Cafter 181 years in same family
OL,6,FWith no heirs, the business was passed
OL,7,Fto his sister's son - Celia and
OL,8,FSharon's grandfather - whose son in
OL,9,Fturn took over, later knocking through
OL,10,Fto the shop next door.
OL,12,FOver the years, the tobacconist
OL,13,Fdiversified to sell souvenirs and
OL,14,Fseaside trinkets.
OL,16,F"We just fell into it really," said
OL,17,FCelia.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
