PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783788475
OL,3,CSeaside souvenir shop shuts its doors
OL,4,Cafter 181 years in same family
OL,6,FShe added their retirement would be
OL,7,Fbittersweet, with the sisters "very
OL,8,Fsad" at leaving behind a chapter which
OL,9,Fhad been "a way of life".
OL,11,F"We've had such lovely people. I think
OL,12,Fit's going to miss people."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
